  </ul>
</nav>


<!-- PAGE 1: HOME -->
<div class="page active" id="page-home">

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-content container">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow fade-up d1">2025 / 2026 Collection</div>
      <h1 class="fade-up d2">Pursuit<br>of<br><span class="gold">Perfection</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub fade-up d3">Where engineering meets artistry. Every Lexus is a testament<br>to the relentless pursuit of the extraordinary.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:16px;" class="fade-up d4">
        <button class="btn btn-solid" onclick="showPage('models')">Explore Models</button>
        <button class="btn" onclick="showPage('gallery')">View Gallery</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Our Philosophy</div>
          <h2>Crafted for Those Who <span class="gold">Demand More</span></h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p class="lead-para">Lexus was born from an audacious challenge — to create the finest automobile ever built. Since 1989, we have done exactly that, model after model, year after year.</p>
          <br>
          <p class="body-para">Every stitch in our leather interiors, every line on our bodywork, and every algorithm in our hybrid systems reflects an uncompromising devotion to quality. Lexus is not simply a car — it is a statement of intent, a declaration of your standards.</p>
          <br><br>
          <button class="btn" onclick="showPage('about')">Our Heritage</button>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="position:relative;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1617469767053-d3b523a0b982?w=700&q=80" alt="Lexus craftsmanship" style="width:100%; display:block; filter:brightness(.85) saturate(.9);">
            <div style="position:absolute; bottom:-20px; right:-20px; width:60%; background:var(--charcoal); border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.2); padding:24px;">
              <div class="section-label" style="font-size:.65rem;">Est. 1989</div>
              <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:1.5rem; color:var(--white);">35 Years of<br><span class="gold">Excellence</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding:0 0 100px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="spec-grid">
        <div class="spec-item"><div class="spec-number">472</div><div class="spec-label">Max Horsepower</div></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><div class="spec-number">3.4<span style="font-size:1.8rem">s</span></div><div class="spec-label">0–100 km/h</div></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><div class="spec-number">12</div><div class="spec-label">Model Lines</div></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><div class="spec-number">70+</div><div class="spec-label">Countries Worldwide</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding:0 0 100px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="highlight-para">"Luxury is not a privilege — it is the natural reward for those who demand nothing less than mastery. At Lexus, every vehicle is a promise: that perfection is possible, and that it is worth pursuing."</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding:0 0 100px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Featured Collection</div>
      <h2>Iconic <span class="gold">Models</span></h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div class="three-col" style="margin-top:48px;">
        <div class="model-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580274455191-1c62238fa333?w=600&q=80" alt="Lexus LS 500">
          <div class="model-card-overlay"><div class="model-price">From KSh 7,500,000</div><div class="model-name">LS 500</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552519507-da3b142c6e3d?w=600&q=80" alt="Lexus IS 500">
          <div class="model-card-overlay"><div class="model-price">From KSh 6,800,000</div><div class="model-name">IS 500</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625047509248-ec889cbff17f?w=600&q=80" alt="Lexus LX 600">
          <div class="model-card-overlay"><div class="model-price">From KSh 12,000,000</div><div class="model-name">LX 600</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:48px;">
        <button class="btn" onclick="showPage('models')">View All Models</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding:0 0 100px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-text">Driving a Lexus is an exercise in controlled exhilaration. Every surface, every response, every moment behind the wheel confirms you made the right choice.</div>
          <div class="testimonial-author">— James Kariuki, Nairobi</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Ownership Experience</div>
          <h3>A Relationship That <span class="gold">Transcends</span> the Drive</h3>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p class="body-para">Lexus ownership is a holistic experience. From the moment you visit a showroom, you are immersed in an ethos of omotenashi — the Japanese art of wholehearted hospitality. Our service advisors, technicians, and concierge teams exist for one purpose only: your complete satisfaction.</p>
          <br>
          <p class="body-para">Every service appointment is a demonstration of respect for your time. Every detail — from the white-gloved handover to the complimentary vehicle health report — is designed to reinforce your confidence in your investment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>


<!-- PAGE 2: MODELS -->
<div class="page" id="page-models">

  <div class="page-banner">
    <div class="bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1617469767053-d3b523a0b982?w=1400&q=80');"></div>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="content container"><div class="section-label">2025 / 2026 Lineup</div><h1>Our <span class="gold">Models</span></h1></div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <p class="lead-para" style="margin-bottom:64px; max-width:60ch;">From the thundering IS 500 F Sport to the serene LS flagship, every model in the Lexus lineup is a complete expression of a distinct character — united by an obsession with quality.</p>

      <div class="section-label">Pricing Overview</div>
