            <h4 style="margin-bottom:16px;">Takumi Craftsmanship</h4>
            <p class="body-para" style="font-size:.9rem;">Every Lexus interior contains details that can only be executed by a Takumi — a master craftsperson who has spent at least 60,000 hours perfecting their art.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom:16px;">Kaizen Philosophy</h4>
            <p class="body-para" style="font-size:.9rem;">Kaizen means continuous improvement — the belief that nothing is ever truly finished. It is why Lexus engineers revisit the same problems every model year.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom:16px;">Monozukuri</h4>
